com.ibm.team.repository.client

Interface ITeamRepository.ILoginHandler.ILoginInfo

  • Enclosing interface:
    ITeamRepository.ILoginHandler

    public static interface ITeamRepository.ILoginHandler.ILoginInfo
    Simple data structure encapsulating both a user id and a password.

    Design note: This is done as an interface so that the implementor has full control over where the user id and password might be stored. #login()will call each of the 2 methods exactly once per login attempt. It would not be unreasonable for a wary client to honor only the first invocation of its methods.
